sentences: Aprilli tegema. Aprilli! (hüüe, kui aprillinali õnnestub).
context: The word 'õnnestub' is the 3rd person singular present tense form of the Estonian verb 'õnestuma', which means to succeed or be successful. It indicates that something works out well or achieves a desired result. In the context provided from the dictionary definition, it appears in the phrase 'kui aprillinali õnnestub' (when an April fool's prank succeeds), showing how this verb is used when referring to whether a trick or joke successfully deceives someone.
